selene (16.2.2) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Changed package dependency to require either libav-tools or ffmpeg

  * Playing the input file will run the media player independently
  without grabbing focus from other windows

  * Show a progress dialog when files are added

  * Add additional columns to the file list view and allow column to be
  re-ordered

  * Added dialog for selecting list view columns

  * Allow columns to be re-ordered from the column selection dialog

  * Various minor changes

